latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY of How to treat Sensitive Skin Burn🥵
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Well Guys this is my very 1st Vlog, If You figure out any mistake else wanna provide any suggestions do let me know, I welcome them honestly 💯
So recently I got ice burn on my face which was completely because of my mistake, and trust me It was so painful and well as I was having burning sensation all over my face. 
So this is the video related to it, that How I got rid off that.
Well Just Cucumber and Water did wonders of me. Nothing else no chemicals, no moisturiser nothing.

You need to keep certain steps inside your mind before doing this:-
1. Make sure you have a Cucumber 🥒 
2.Wash your face with lukewarm water, You didn’t need to apply face wash 🧼 3.Once you apply it gently on your face you need to keep that for 15 minutes 
4. After that you need to remove it from your face using a clean towel else your hand, you don’t have to use water again to wash your face. Just simply remove them and after that you need not to apply any cream or moisturiser let your skin breath.

Also Cucumber is Boasting anti-inflammatory properties, as well as antioxidants and nutrients like vitamin C and folic acid, cucumbers make a nourishing ingredient for a face mask, and a good base for adding other ingredients that can benefit your skin, like honey, aloe vera, or oatmeal and has many other benefits.
 
Do watch this till end. 
Like, Comment and Share. Show some love so that I get motivation to make many other video’s.
Thank you ❤️
